---
title: Pesto Baked Sea Bass and Warm Tomato Salsa with Rosemary Potatoes and Lemon Dressed Baby Leaf Salad
description: Classic green pesto, fragrant with basil, is paired with an easy tomato salsa for an Italian inspired meal. In this Pesto Baked Basa and Warm Tomato Salsa, the white fish is perfect for soaking up the delicious flavour.
